      <title>General Atlantic 将以 500 亿美元的价格收购 Partners Capital 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/general-atlantic-to-buy-a-stake-in-50-billion-partners-capital</link>
