      <title>由于高利率的影响，更多英国买房出租抵押贷款出现拖欠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/more-uk-buy-to-let-mortgages-dip-into-arrears-as-high-rates-bite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于高利率和更严格的监管给房东带来压力，2023 年最后一个季度英国拖欠的买房出租抵押贷款数量激增 18%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/more-uk-buy-to-let-mortgages-dip-into-arrears-as-high-rates-bite</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 10:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
